# Skeleton key / generator internals -- NEVER published. The generator's
# publish step (sastgenerator: scripts/publish_benchmark.py) uses an allowlist
# and is the primary guard; these patterns are the git-layer backstop so an
# accidental wholesale copy + `git add` can never stage the answer internals.
# (*.sarif above already covers expected_perfect.sarif.)
